        </div>
        <h2 class="covid"><b>Response of UON to COVID-19</b></h2>
        <h4 class="covid">
            University of Newcastle is implementing a phased recovery of university operations. <br />
            We are currently in Stage 3 of the restart process.
        </h4>
        <a href="blank" target="_blank"><p class="covid_link">More about UON‘s response to COVID-19</p></a>
    </div>
    <div class="p3">
        <div class="p3-txt">
            <div class="p3-img">
                <img src="/images/index/1.jpeg" alt="title logo 1" width="350" height="300" />
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2 class="p3-title">To-Do List </h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p3-txt">
            <div class="p3-img">
                <img src="/images/index/1.jpeg" alt="title logo 1" width="350" height="300" />
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2 class="p3-title">Common Questions </h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p3-txt">
            <div class="p3-img">
                <img src="/images/index/1.jpeg" alt="title logo 1" width="350" height="300" />
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2 class="p3-title">About COVID-19 </h2>
